Package com.google.gdata.data.spreadsheet

Class Summary
Cell GData schema extension describing a spreadsheet formula.
CellEntry Atom Entry for a single cell for the Google Spreadsheets cells feed.
CellFeed The feed for spreadsheet cells of Google Spreadsheets.
ColCount GData schema extension describing a spreadsheet's column count.
CustomElementCollection Extension that globs together all "gsx:" tags into one.
ListEntry Atom Entry for one single row Google Spreadsheets in the list-based access mode.
ListFeed The feed for treating a spreadsheet as a collection of list items.
Namespaces GData namespace definitions related to Google Spreadsheets.
RowCount GData schema extension describing a spreadsheet's row count.
SpreadsheetEntry One spreadsheet, when listing all spreadsheets you have access to.
SpreadsheetFeed The feed for getting a list of Spreadsheets within a sheet.
WorksheetEntry One worksheet, when listing all worksheets within a spreadsheet.
WorksheetFeed The feed for getting a list of worksheets within a sheet.
